Tornado Blog App

(c) Vladyslav Ishchenko 12.2014
====================================

Steck of Tech

Backend:
	Main framefork: Tornado
	DB: Riack

Frontend:
	Backbonejs
	Marionettejs
	Backbone-relations
	Bootstrap from Twitter:
		Project layout:
			https://github.com/ironsummitmedia/startbootstrap-clean-blog/


1. Install prerequisites and build tornado


2. Install DB


3. Install project prerequisites
	pip install -r

5. Run the blog example
   cd 
   ./app.py
   If need chmod +x app.py


6. Go to the site

   http://localhost:8888/
